I was one of those who didn't know, I found out now that you said ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif ":P")  

I know what part you're talking about, but since I found SSTU I dropped KW, so I don't use them anymore ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif ":P")  

also, instead of adding a part with a reaction wheel, I made this:

    @PART[ABL_LFO_A|ABL_5tank9|ABL_5tank18|ABL_5tank_nose|ABL_adapter_5_3|ABL_5tank4|ABL_adapter_5_2|ABL_LFO_C|ABL_LFO_B]:FINAL
    {MODULE{ 	name = ModuleReactionWheel		PitchTorque = 500	YawTorque = 500	RollTorque = 500	RESOURCE	{		name = ElectricCharge		rate = 0.0001	}}
    }

I basically added reaction wheels to every tank in the AB Launcher pack so they could carry the freaking Buran ![:P](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif ":P") (and made them cost virtually nothing because that's what the game gets for not giving me gimbal trimming, and because I don't know if I can remove that cost....)
